OL,5,Criots
OL,7,FA year later, he remains housed in a
OL,8,Fhotel; new protests are happening, and
OL,9,Fauthorities fear a repeat of last
OL,10,Fsummer's violence.
OL,12,F"It was a tough time," he told ITV
OL,13,FNews. "There were rumours for a long
OL,14,Ftime...still I avoid some places
OL,15,Fbecause of those issues ... I'm still
OL,16,Fa bit worried."
OL,18,FHe is not alone.
