OL,5,Criots
OL,7,FIn Epping, protests broke out outside
OL,8,Fthe Bell hotel after a 38-year-old
OL,9,Fasylum seeker was charged with sexual
OL,10,Fassault, something he denies.
OL,12,FEight police officers were injured
OL,13,Foutside the hotel, as well as two
OL,14,Fhotel employees. Five men were charged
OL,15,Fwith disorder at the protests.
OL,17,FEssex police are urging restraint
OL,18,Famong politicians and protestors alike.
OL,20,FMeanwhile they are bracing for more
OL,21,Funrest.
