OL,7,FIn a statement, the Refugee Council
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our frontline staff work in
OL,9,Fmany of the communities affected and
OL,10,Fsee that most people are fair-minded
OL,11,Fand compassionate.
OL,13,F"While they may have valid questions
